Ethel Shannon (May 22, 1898 – July 10, 1951) was an American actress. She appeared in over 30 silent movies in the early 20th century. ( for stage_and_film_actress_Effie_Shannon , see Effie_Shannon ) Ethel_Shannon ( May_22_,_1898 – July_10_,_1951 ) was an_American_actress .
